
Ranger Help for: forage
=======================

SYNTAX:      forage
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE EXP:    NA
BASE SP:     variable

SUMMARY:    
This task allows a follower to go find the nearest wilderness area
and forage for food and bring it back to you to eat. How nourishing
the food is that the follower brings back depends on how smart the
follower is. This is a hard task to teach, so only the smartest
followers will be able to learn it.

